  <brief_title>High-intensity Versus Conventional-intensity Noninvasive Positive Pressure Ventilation in Acute Exacerbation of Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease: the HAPPEN Study (HAPPEN)</brief_title>
  <official_title>High-intensity Versus Conventional-intensity Noninvasive Positive Pressure Ventilation in Acute Exacerbation of Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease: a Multicenter, Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
